Privacy Statement &nbsp; This privacy policy will explain how mri4all.org uses personal data we collect from you when you use our website. &nbsp;
How do we collect your data? You directly provide mri4all.org with the data we collect. We collect data and process data only when you complete the questionnaire regarding your intention to participate in the MRI4ALL hackathon. &nbsp;
How will we use your data? mri4all.org collects your data so that collect applications for the participation in the planned hackathon event.
